# Single-File App Logic

All application logic must live in `index.php`. No separate PHP files for app logic.

## Allowed

- `index.php` — routing, handlers, helpers, config, HTML
- `config.php` — optional override (merged into CONFIG)
- `pb_migrations/*.js` — PocketBase schema
- `scripts/*` — shell scripts only (e.g. download-pocketbase.sh, start.sh)

## Not Allowed

- `scripts/*.php` — no PHP scripts; add handlers in `index.php` (minimal app has no CLI commands)
- Separate PHP files for features, helpers, or API handlers

## Adding New Logic

Put new functions and request handlers in `index.php`. Optional CLI entrypoints may use `PHP_SAPI === 'cli'` when needed.
